org.debugtrace

Class DebugTrace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.debugtrace.DebugTrace

  • public class DebugTrace
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class for debugging.
    Call DebugTrace.enter and DebugTrace.leave methods when enter and leave your methods, then outputs execution trace of the program.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Masato Kokubo
